<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313776' id='t-313776'>I saw my first Apple computer in 1984,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='320635' id='t-320635'>and I thought to myself,</span>
