<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611139' id='t-611139'>This technology that fascinated me in 1987</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614722' id='t-614722'>is now on my iPhone and on yours as well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618443' id='t-618443'>But, you know, I find reading with machines</span>
