<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702533' id='t-702533'>that aren't labeled and buttons that aren't labeled,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705484' id='t-705484'>and that's why the World Wide Web Consortium 3,</span>
