<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='855158' id='t-855158'>I wonder what the future will hold.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='858166' id='t-858166'>The technology will advance even further,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861857' id='t-861857'>but I can still remember my mum saying, 60 years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='865525' id='t-865525'>&quot;Remember, darling,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='867459' id='t-867459'>you'll never be able to read the print with your fingers.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='871604' id='t-871604'>I'm so glad that the interaction between braille transcribers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876781' id='t-876781'>volunteer readers and passionate inventors,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879678' id='t-879678'>has allowed this dream of reading to come true for me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='882868' id='t-882868'>and for blind people throughout the world.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885872' id='t-885872'>I'd like to thank my researcher Hannah Martin,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='889518' id='t-889518'>who is my slide clicker, who clicks the slides,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='892488' id='t-892488'>and my wife, Professor Mary Crock, who's the light of my life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='896879' id='t-896879'>is coming on to collect me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='898237' id='t-898237'>I want to thank her too.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='899432' id='t-899432'>I think I have to say goodbye now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='901432' id='t-901432'>Bless you. Thank you very much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
